<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email</title>
    <style>
        <%- emailStyles %>
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="icon-large">✉️</div>
            <h1>Verify Your Email Address</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p class="greeting">Hi <%= name %>,</p>
            
            <p class="message">
                Thanks for signing up with Event Manager! We're excited to have you on board.
            </p>

            <p class="message">
                To complete your registration and access all features, please verify your email address 
                by clicking the button below:
            </p>

            <div class="verification-box text-center">
                <a href="<%= verificationUrl %>" class="cta-button cta-button-large">Verify Email Address</a>
                
                <p class="alternative-text">
                    Or copy and paste this link into your browser:
                </p>
                <div class="verification-link">
                    <%= verificationUrl %>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="warning-box">
                <strong>⚠️ Security Note:</strong><br>
                This verification link will expire in 24 hours for security purposes. 
                If you didn't create an account with Event Manager, please ignore this email.
            </div>

            <p class="message">
                Once verified, you'll have full access to all features including:
                • Event creation and management
                • Team collaboration tools
                • Task tracking and analytics
            </p>

            <p class="message">
                Best regards,<br>
                <strong>The Event Manager Team</strong>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>© <%= year %> Event Manager. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p class="mt-15 font-12 color-muted">
                If you're having trouble clicking the button, copy and paste the URL above into your web browser.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
